data.description: This expansive 6-bedroom home offers a captivating view of the mountains, a beautifully finished walk-out basement, and  a meticulously landscaped backyard. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the main living areas, creating a sense of  fluidity and versatility throughout the home. Large windows allow the warmth of natural light into every room. Escape to  the tranquility of your primary suite, where the en-suite bathroom boasts a soaking tub, separate shower, double vanity,  and generous closet space with dual closets. Step outside into your very own private oasis. Whether you're savoring your  morning coffee on the patio or hosting a vibrant summer barbecue, you'll relish the serene ambiance of this outdoor  retreat. Don't miss this opportunity to call this remarkable Colorado Springs residence your own! Reach out to us today to  arrange a showing.
